HEADWORD: Nonyl
<hw>Non"yl</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[<ets>Non</ets>ane +
<ets>-yl</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>The hydrocarbon radical,
<chform>C9H19-</chform>, derived from nonane and forming many compounds.
Used also adjectively; <as>as, <ex>nonyl</ex> alcohol</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
